### CashWise API Testing
### Use this with VS Code REST Client extension or Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = your_token_here

### 1. Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Salman Dowaik",
  "email": "salman@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "salman@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Get All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Income Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/type/INCOME
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Expense Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/type/EXPENSE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Create Income Transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000.000,
  "type": "INCOME",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "description": "Monthly salary",
  "transactionDate": "2026-02-01",
  "isManual": true
}

### 7. Create Expense Transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 45.500,
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "categoryId": 5,
  "description": "Lunch at Nando's with team",
  "transactionDate": "2026-02-26",
  "isManual": true
}

### 8. Create More Expenses for Testing
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 120.000,
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "categoryId": 6,
  "description": "Taxi to work",
  "transactionDate": "2026-02-25",
  "isManual": true
}

### 9. Get All Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Get Transactions by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/range?startDate=2026-02-01&endDate=2026-02-28
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Get Dashboard Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Get Dashboard Stats for Specific Period
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats?startDate=2026-02-01&endDate=2026-02-28
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Update Transaction (replace {id} with actual transaction ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/transactions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50.000,
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "categoryId": 5,
  "description": "Updated: Lunch at Nando's",
  "transactionDate": "2026-02-26",
  "isManual": true
}

### 14. Delete Transaction (replace {id} with actual transaction ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transactions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
